---
import TuiLayout from '../layouts/TuiLayout.astro';
---
<TuiLayout title="Home" section="home">
  <h1>@neftaly/sigil</h1>
  <p>React renderer for character-grid UIs. Renders to DOM, terminal, or Three.js.</p>

  <h2>Hello world</h2>
  <pre><code>import {'{'} Box, Text {'}'} from '@neftaly/sigil'
import {'{'} CharuiCanvas {'}'} from '@neftaly/sigil/dom'

&lt;CharuiCanvas width={'{'}40{'}'} height={'{'}10{'}'}&gt;
  &lt;Box border="single" padding={'{'}1{'}'}&gt;
    &lt;Text&gt;Hello world&lt;/Text&gt;
  &lt;/Box&gt;
&lt;/CharuiCanvas&gt;</code></pre>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                      │
│  Hello world                         │
│                                      │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘</pre>

  <h2>Widgets</h2>
  <p>16 components. Each takes <code>value</code> + <code>onChange</code>.</p>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup"><span class="focused">╭────────────────────────────────╮</span>   [x] Shielded    ●━━ Dark mode
<span class="focused">│</span>John Smith█                     <span class="focused">│</span>   ( ) Option A
<span class="focused">╰────────────────────────────────╯</span>   (o) Option B    ├████████░░░░┤ 64%

┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐         Loading... ⠹
│ Save     │  │ Cancel   │</pre>

  <h2>Surfaces</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Import</th><th>Output</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>@neftaly/sigil/dom</code></td><td>Canvas element + hidden ARIA elements</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>@neftaly/sigil/terminal</code></td><td>ANSI output, alternate screen buffer</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>@neftaly/sigil/threedee</code></td><td>3D grid (React Three Fiber)</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

